Siam: a chacun son royaume

Travel Documentary hosted by Georges Pernoud, published by TV5Monde broadcasted as part of TV5Monde Thalassa series in 2016 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/0/0e/Siam-a-chacun-son-royaume-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Siam, to each his kingdom.

For centuries, Siam was the richest kingdom and most powerful of Southeast Asia, for spices, gold or its porcelain. Today is for its white sand beaches, lush nature and delicious cuisine that this part of Asia still makes us dream.
